    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and truly looks as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. It has been meticulously maintained, with a flawless exterior paint finish that shines perfectly and an interior that shows virtually no signs of wear. Every feature, from the advanced electronics to the premium upholstery, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is sound, having received regular servicing that ensures it drives as smoothly as the day it was first purchased. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a used car in truly impeccable, like-new condition.",
