    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that\u2019s perfect for someone looking for value! This vehicle is a functional, honest performer that has served its previous owners well and is ready for its next chapter. While it shows some clear signs of its journey through visible cosmetic wear and a few minor mechanical quirks, it remains a solid choice for a daily driver or a first car. If you're looking for a practical vehicle with character at a great price, this is the one for you!",
      "price": 18500.0,
