    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained and climate-control garaged since day one. The exterior retains its original deep luster, with a mirror-like paint finish entirely free of swirls, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and all tactile surfaces feel factory-fresh. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It features a complete, documented service history performed exclusively at authorized centers, ensuring every component operates with precision. From the whisper-quiet idle to the seamless gear transitions, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved example that satisfies the most demanding standards of excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
